               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360201-name-143" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-143" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-143" type="surname" value="STEWART"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-143" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN STEWART</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a tailor, and live in Cheapside, On the 21st of January, about a quarter to one o'clock, I was in my shop—my attention was drawn to a bustle at the door—I went and saw a cloak lying on the payment—two gentleman said a man had run away with some cloak—I saw the prisoner running away with a cloak, lined with red, over his arm—the policeman caught him, and brought him to me with it—it had been on a block inside the door.</p>
