                  </hi>. I am servant to Mr. Stewart. I was walking in Cheap<lb></lb>side, and saw the prisoner run away from my master's door with a cloak over his arm—I pursed, and was present when the policeman took him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
